name: F1Deck
0:
”Alexa, ask F1Deck for information on the drivers championship”
”Alexa, ask F1Deck where is Lewis Hamilton in the standings”
”Alexa, ask F1Deck how many points Mercedes have in the championship”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: f. one deck
des:
F1Deck has Formula 1 news, standings, races for both the drivers & constructors championships. and all drivers & teams.

You can use this skill on any alexa/echo device. Just ask one of the sample phrases to test it out

For more information please visit F1Deck.com 

Not affiliated with Formula One World Championship.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
